🏛️ Project Name: Nyay AI — AI-Powered Legal Learning & Case Collaboration Platform

Simple Explanation (Hinglish):
Nyay AI ek smart platform hai jahan law students aur AI milke real legal cases par kaam karte hain. Iska main purpose hai law students ko real-world legal experience dena aur logon ko legal help provide karna — wo bhi fast aur easy way me.

User apni legal problem platform par likhta hai, phir law student AI ke help se us case ko analyze karta hai, uske liye report ya advice banata hai. AI system jaise Gemini help karta hai — legal reasoning, citation, aur analysis me.

Jo case solve hota hai, wo public case library me upload hota hai, jisse dusre students bhi seekh sakte hain aur pichle cases padh sakte hain.
Law students ke liye ye ek learning + earning opportunity bhi hai — wo real cases par kaam karke paise kama sakte hain aur experience gain karte hain.

Nyay AI ethical aur privacy-focused hai — user ka data anonymous rehta hai, par case educational purpose ke liye available hota hai.

In short:

Nyay AI ek platform hai jahan AI aur law students milkar real legal problems solve karte hain, logon ko madad milti hai, students seekhte hain aur earn bhi karte hain — sab kuch ek digital legal ecosystem ke andar.
